MaaS Location SDK

Packages 
Package Description
com.phunware.location
MaaSLocation SDK, provides highly reusable location related class and functions
com.phunware.location.bluedot
Provides BlueDot functionality for PwMseLocation Provider
com.phunware.location.manager
Provides location managers, used in PwLocationProviderFactory to create those location providers.
com.phunware.location.provider
Provides abstract and pre-defined location providers, also provides PwLocationProviderFactory to create those location providers.
com.phunware.location.provider.interceptor
Provides interceptors to inject PwFloorId into location object.
